data.text:
Hey all,

I am wanting to sell my license of Spectrasonics Omnisphere 2 license. After purchasing during Covid and using sparingly (silly of me to buy) it's just been collecting dust in a cupboard.

I would be open to selling this for £300 (OPEN TO OFFERS) and I would cover the transfer fee myself to make the offer more attractive.

Spectrasonics have a thorough license transfer process and this is all handled by them so it's 100% secure.

Spectrasonics are wanting the following information;

Buyer's Name:

Buyer's Email:

Buyer's Username created at Spectrasonics website:

Buyer’s Address:

If anyone is intrested at all and would like a chat about it please let me know!

Thanks
